description: Two blurry, light-colored shapes appear against a grainy, dark background.
A blurry, grainy, black and white image appears to show a crowd of people gathered in front of a building at night.
The image shows the partially visible black letters "EXD" painted on a grayish-white surface.
A grainy, black and white image shows a crowd of people, some holding signs, gathered around a car at night.
A grainy black and white image shows a person wearing glasses speaking into a megaphone.
A grainy, black and white image appears to show a group of people.
A grainy, black and white image depicts a group of people, some of whom appear to be holding torches or flags.
This is a dark image with some blurry, lighter-colored spots or patches and a grainy texture throughout.
The image shows a black surface with small, light-colored speckles throughout.
A textured, off-white surface with faint vertical lines and small imperfections is visible.
A blurry, grainy image shows bright, out-of-focus lights against a dark background.
A grainy, black and white image appears to show the top of a submarine or similar vessel in the water.
A dark, grainy image shows a blurry, vertical streak of light and some other indistinct shapes.
A grainy black and white image shows a person lying down, their face partially obscured by shadow and their hand raised near their face.
A blurry, gray surface, possibly concrete, is visible.
A grainy, black and white image shows a group of people, some holding signs and appearing to be protesting.
Gray smoke-like clouds move across a black background.
A grainy, black and white image shows a person with glasses raising their right arm.
A plain, off-white surface with faint lines and small specks is visible.
White particles fall and gather on a dark surface.
A grainy, black and white close-up shows a person wearing glasses and speaking into a microphone.
A grainy, black and white image appears to show a snow-covered bridge at night.
A grainy, black and white image shows a group of men, seemingly talking.
A dark, grainy image shows blurry light-colored shapes that resemble clouds or smoke.
A blurry, grainy, gray surface has a darker, circular smudge on the lower right side.
